headline.main: Gen. Walker's Expedition.; PARTICULARS OF THE CAPTURE OF TRUXILLO NAMES OF THE WOUNDED.

docs.lead_paragraph: The schooner Dewdrop, Capt. TERRY, arrived at this port this morning, from Ruatan Island the l6th inst. Among the passengers is a gentleman who left Truxillo on the l2th. From him we have full partic ulars of the capture of that city, and a full narrative of the events up to the latest dates.
